text: Chishma () is a rural locality (a village) in Shulganovsky Selsoviet, Tatyshlinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 48 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 41 km from Verkhniye Tatyshly, 1 km from Shulganovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tatyshlinsky District
title: Chishma, Tatyshlinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
